8. Monitoring Strategy Health
Daily Checklist:
Review portfolio_signals.txt for position changes
Check Sharpe ratios (all should be >0.8 ideally)
Monitor danger scores and position adjustments
Weekly Checklist:
Review reconciliation email
If drift <5pp: No action needed ✅
If drift 5-10pp: Monitor, check again next week ⚠️
If drift >10pp: Investigate data changes 🚨
Alert Thresholds:
Sharpe drops below 0.5: Review asset strategy
MaxDD exceeds -15%: Consider reducing position sizing
Drift exceeds 10pp: Check for data corrections/backfills
Multiple assets declining: Possible market regime change
9. Initial Setup
When starting with the position history system:
Option A: Start Fresh
Delete existing position_history.csv (if any)
Run production mode
System starts from 0% and builds positions over days
Option B: Initialize with Current Positions
Create position_history.csv with actual current positions
Set date to yesterday
Production mode continues from those positions
